06:09.000 --> 06:11.000
What story do you have for us today?

06:11.000 --> 06:13.000
Well, it's actually not a story.

06:13.000 --> 06:14.000
It's a fact.

06:14.000 --> 06:16.000
I mean, people in Egypt, when they're sick,

06:16.000 --> 06:18.000
they never call in sick themselves.

06:18.000 --> 06:21.000
They'll have someone do that for them.

06:21.000 --> 06:22.000
Oh, that's interesting.

06:22.000 --> 06:24.000
Why? Why do they do this?

06:24.000 --> 06:27.000
Well, there's this weird speculation about, you know,

